title: IAA Tonight | NBA Legend Vince Carter
description: 8x NBA All-Star and dunk legend Vince Carter joined Adam Pacman Jones, Leger Douzable, and Omar Kelly to discuss perhaps the all-time greatest dunk contest performance at 2000 All-Star Weekend, dunking over Frédéric Weis of France in the 2000 Summer Olympics, and his new podcast. Plus, Where will Jimmy G land next as the world awaits the 49ers QB to be traded.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Vince Carter, Adam Pacman Jones, Leger Douzable, Omar Kelly)
